<D>__{even if the operation's successful that is, if he lives i think he'll be paralyzed for life.}
<C>__{willie}
<D>__{you'll do everything you can, won't you? anything between you and me.. that won't count, will it? it doesn't have to. look, doc, anything you want in the world you just ask for it and you got it. go on, doc... ask for it.}
